values
  ('yacht-charter-luxury-experience-websites-dubai', 'Websites for Dubai Yacht Charters & Luxury Experiences', 'Selling a Dubai yacht charter online means selling a feeling at a high price. Here''s what a luxury experience website needs to convert discerning clients.', $body$A Dubai yacht charter, a private desert dinner, a helicopter tour — these aren't products, they're moments, sold at premium prices to discerning, often international clients. The website has to make someone *feel* the experience before they'll pay for it, then make booking it feel as effortless and exclusive as the experience itself.

